{"tid":1494752,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(Twitter超新手攻略)估唔到文宣都可以咁好玩","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:09:23.000Z","uid":184581,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9779e30a9f4ab2c374cb5277c4e72f660eef5f96","tid":1494752,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:43:28.000Z","msg":"其實Twitter好易用仲好好玩成隻<span style=\"color: red;\">養成game咁</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n超新手攻略<br />\n第一步:右上打lihkg<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWMxv0H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWMxv0H.png&h=5cf3fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二步:見到有志同道合既人唔理3721就Follow佢同比個心心佢(好多時間d人見到你follow佢同比心佢 人地就會follow番你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CPOOOp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CPOOOp.png&h=a5bc522f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三步:見到主要要文宣or 有用既野就retweet佢比多d人睇到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gm2gXHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgm2gXHP.png&h=93be9c4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第四步:仲可以用#xxxxx 去tag一d group(呢加主要既係#EYEOFHK<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sj5irCv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSj5irCv.png&h=9f6af521&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n技巧:1.最好用英文 因為twitter既主要用家都係外國人<br />\n        2.英文唔太得既可以only用like同retweet<br />\n        3.愈多人follow你 你retweet果時就愈多人見到 影響力就愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n        4.如果follow你既人有&gt;70(唔好太少 佢地會覺係假AC)見到D出名既外國人開post就沖入去like入面D人(有時時候佢地會follow返你)<br />\n        5.如果你個AC有好多外國人Follow既 咁你成功做到一個輸出文宣既AC喇!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n        6.改下個人資料先(個AC靚靚仔仔先有人Follow加麻)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n注意:有樣野盡量唔好做 1.#xxxx 唔好超過2個 因為太多就會比人話惡意洗版 會比人罵<br />\n                                      2. 盡量唔好用 @xxxxx 呢個多數係TAG比D 朋友同政客既<br />\n<br />\n4日既成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dP1UKuh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdP1UKuh.png&h=eddd414b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0477bb53f0570bbf5c6620529e60eb264a71eacb","tid":1494752,"uid":204626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"038c897d082a7d9e6046c7c4025ea8ddfc86d34e","tid":1494752,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"聽d老手話 twitter有個熱門既功能 <br />\n如果一個tag #xxxxx 係一定時間內勁多人retweet同po野就會全世界都見到"},{"pid":"6d091980d2d112c905d191ed8cea669f7d27c910","tid":1494752,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:48:51.000Z","msg":"唉,毒撚玩唔掂呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個account 12年用到依家,都無你咁多followers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac3577bba3275f4f3ce19e97900eb9a33a64434","tid":1494752,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d091980d2d112c905d191ed8cea669f7d27c910","tid":1494752,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:48:51.000Z","msg":"唉,毒撚玩唔掂呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我個account 12年用到依家,都無你咁多followers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:50:18.000Z","msg":"好易加姐<br />\n其實我都冇咩點留言<br />\n9成都係LIKE人同RETWEET人 冇啦啦比人FOLLOW"},{"pid":"a9ac1d481bcd9667f000b81e37c1fa1e427faa7f","tid":1494752,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ac3577bba3275f4f3ce19e97900eb9a33a64434","tid":1494752,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d091980d2d112c905d191ed8cea669f7d27c910","tid":1494752,"uid":63626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:48:51